profile:
I am an electrical engineer through my academic background. I provide residential and commercial services in the installation, diagnosis, solutions design, system design of audio and video systems. 

Whether it be digital signage, video walls, complicated video distribution systems, audio distribution systems I can provide consultation, installations, fixes and upgrades.

My clients in the past have included clinics, stores in malls, offices, restaurants as well as residences.

Feel free to contact me if something is not working or you want to install something or upgrade something or just want a second opinion.
